---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Core Principles | Jamal Williams">
	<section class="space-y-12 py-20 animate-fade-in">
		<header class="space-y-4">
			<a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>
				Back Home
			</a>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl font-display animate-slide-up">
				Core <span class="text-gradient">Principles</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
				The internal compass that guides every project, partnership, and line of code.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="space-y-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
			<!-- Freedom -->
			<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-4 border-blue-500">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">Freedom</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					I want the ability to choose my life and how I live it. That means ensuring I have good options at all times and I'm never in a situation where I'm forced to do the things I don't want to.
				</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
					<div class="bg-blue-500/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
						<span class="text-blue-400 font-bold block mb-1">In Practice</span>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Choosing where I live and work; building systems that provide leverage and time.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-red-500/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
						<span class="text-red-400 font-bold block mb-1">The Shadow</span>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Dependency on a single source of income or location; lacking the resources to choose.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Integrity -->
			<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">Integrity</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					I want to do things in a way that I'm proud of. I want to engage in good faith and deliver on my word.
				</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
					<div class="bg-emerald-500/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
						<span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold block mb-1">In Practice</span>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Engaging in good faith; delivering on promises; doing things the right way even when it's harder.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-red-500/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
						<span class="text-red-400 font-bold block mb-1">The Shadow</span>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Taking unnecessary shortcuts; agreeing to things I cannot do.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Responsibility -->
			<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-4 border-purple-500">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-display mb-4">Responsibility</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
					I take ownership of the things in my life—both the good and the bad. Sovereign people don't make excuses; they make adjustments.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<footer class="pt-12 text-center">
			<a href="/bio" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">Read the Origin Story →</a>
		</footer>
	</section>
</Layout>
